arts.ttl: Accrington Stanley vs Oldham Athletic: The hosts progress after superb first-half display
arts.sum: A dominant first half from the hosts proved the decisive factor in this game as Anjola Popoola, Kelsey Mooney and Josh Woods had John Doolan's side up by three at the break. What initially looked like a shot from Kelsey Mooney soon turned into a good ball across the box to Anjola Popoola.
